products.title: Rio Blackout Solar Ivory Neat Fit Honeycomb Pleated Blind
products.description: Rio blackout solar is a honeycomb blackout pleated fabric, available in a wide range of tropical colours with an added bonus of a solar silver backing to block harmful uv rays. One of their lightest cream shades in the neat fit range, rio ivory could be used as a eye-catching feature piece or used to just help blend a theme together. Product id: db-nfpl0035 fabric colour: ivory material: 100% polyester lining: reflective blackout silver backing - uv blocking headrail: white neat fit hardware with slide-in clips control type: folding pull down handle, minimum projection from glass to front of handle is 30mm.
